"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.14.1.8\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.14.1.8</span> 标题：在本章其他地方讨论过的圣殿其他建筑物和构件</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">梁木 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5.3 大梁、梁木、椽子 (crossbeam, rafter)&lt;REALIA:3.1.5.3&gt;</a></h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>链子 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.21.4 锁链、链子 (chain)&lt;REALIA:3.21.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>庭院 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.20 院子、院宇、宫廷 (courtyard, court)&lt;REALIA:3.20&gt;</a></p>\n<p>门 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2 门、门口 (door, doorway)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>门柱 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.4 门柱 (doorpost)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>堡垒 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.2 要塞、堡垒、城堡 (fortress, stronghold, castle, citadel, fort)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>地基 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.1 地基、根基、基础 (foundation)&lt;REALIA:3.1.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>大门／城门 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5 城门 (city gate)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>门口 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.3 房屋或建筑群的大门或大门入口 (gate or gateway to house or building complex)&lt;REALIA:3.1.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>护卫室 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.13.3.5.2 护卫室、守卫房 (guardroom)&lt;REALIA:3.13.3.5.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>合页、铰链 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.3 合页 (hinge)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.3&gt;</a></p>\n<p>圣所 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.1 圣所、圣洁的地方 (Holy Place)&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.1&gt;</a></p>\n<p>门楣 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.5 门楣 (lintel)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>至圣所 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.15.2.2 至圣所、最圣洁的地方 (Holy of Holies, Most Holy Place)&lt;REALIA:3.15.2.2&gt;</a></p>\n<p>柱顶上的网 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 柱子、柱顶 (column, pillar, capital)&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>柱子 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.5 柱子、柱顶 (column, pillar, capital)&lt;REALIA:3.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>屋顶 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.5 屋顶、房顶 (roof, housetop)&lt;REALIA:3.1.5&gt;</a></p>\n<p>楼梯、台阶、阶梯 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.7 楼梯、台阶、阶梯 (stairs, steps)&lt;REALIA:3.1.7&gt;</a></p>\n<p>楼层 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.3 墙 (wall)&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.3&gt;</a> 和<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.6.4 楼上的房间、楼房、屋顶的房间 (upper room, roof chamber)&lt;REALIA:3.1.6.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>门槛 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2.6 门槛 (threshold, doorsill)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2.6&gt;</a></p>\n<p>窗户 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.4 窗户 (window)&lt;REALIA:3.1.4&gt;</a></p>\n<p>墙 - <a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.6 边界墙、围墙、围栏、栅栏 (boundary wall, fence)&lt;REALIA:3.6&gt;</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>",
